content: v1xingyue: Merged 3 significant PRs this week, including a feature for Aggregator swap of SUI tokens (#3012, +572/-77 lines), axios implementation for price fetching with private key support (#2879, +234770/-12659 lines), and post-release fixes (#3141, +6304/-643 lines). Also opened PR #3131 to fix a Gitpod installation bug and provided one code review, with activity spread across 3 days of the week.
